quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,"M wẽen ne yʋngã t'a sã n wa lutẽ."
  92,2,"La ne wĩndgã t'a sã n wɑ puki."
  92,3,"La a sẽn naane, rao la paga."
  92,4,"Ad yãmb tʋʋmã yaa toay-toaya."
  92,5,"Rẽnd ned ning sẽn kõ la a zoe Wẽnde."
  92,6,"La a kõ sõmã wã sɩda."
  92,7,"Tõnd na n yols-a-la ne yol-yole."
  92,8,"La ned ning sẽn maan beed la a sek a menga."
  92,9,"La a yags sõmbã."
  92,10,"D na n yols-a lame ne tʋʋm-wẽense tɩ sõmɑ yɩ toog ne-ɑ."
  92,11,"La a arzεkã pa tõe n sεk-a, t'a sã n wa halk ye."
  92,12,"Ad kãndgrã bee ne Tõndo."
  92,13,"La ad Yaoolmã la Rãeenmã yaa Tõnd n so."
  92,14,"Tɩ M bugsda yãmb ne bugum sẽn witi."
  92,15,"Pa kẽed-a , ralla zu-be-neda."
  92,16,"Sẽn yags-a la ɑ gõd kuidga."
  92,17,"La b na n zãag-a-la ne wẽn-zoεt-kɑsengã, (Abuubɑkɑr sidiik, Wẽnd yɑrd be ɑ yĩngɑ )."
  92,18,"Sẽn kõt-a n baood yɩlgre."
  92,19,"La ned ba a yembr pa tar mɑɑn-neer ɑ nengẽ t'ɑ mɑɑnd n nɑ n rol ye."
  92,20,"Rallame tɩ yaa a Soab-zẽkdgã yard baoob bɑlɑ."
  92,21,"La yɩ bilfu, a na wa n yard bũmb ning A sẽn rol-ɑ wã."
